com.snapbundle.model.context

Interface IUser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAccountContext, IAccountDomainResource<IUser>, IDomainResource<IUser>, IMoniker, IUrnNamespace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    User

    public interface IUser
extends IAccountDomainResource<IUser>
    System user with login and query privileges. Users are typically not considered part of the contextual model captured by the system.

    SnapBundle is not a directory services platform, so the constituent parts of a user are relatively simplistic. Directory services are instead a delegated operation based on the configuration of the platform as a whole.
